# References Directory

Place documentation and reference material here for Codex to consult as needed.

## When to use

- API documentation
- Database schemas
- Company policies
- Domain-specific knowledge
- Detailed workflow guides

## Best practices

1. Keep files under 10k words when possible
2. Include table of contents for files >100 lines
3. Reference directly from SKILL.md (one level deep)
4. Avoid duplication with SKILL.md content
